{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">PARTIDO REGIONALISTA INDEPENDIENTE</div></div>", "i": 9641055}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Don Humberto de la Maza Maillet y Eduardo Salas Cerda, Presidente y Secretario General de la Directiva Central; y el se&#xF1;or Mario Gonz&#xE1;lez Rubio, Secretario del Tribunal Supremo, respectivamente, del Partido Regionalista Independiente, han informado la nueva composici&#xF3;n de la colectividad:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  DIRECTIVA CENTRAL:</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Presidente&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Humberto Osvaldo de la Maza Maillet</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Primera Vicepresidenta&nbsp; Alejandra Mar&#xED;a Bravo Hidaldo</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Segundo Vicepresidente&nbsp; Ra&#xFA;l Luis Fernando Herrera Herrera</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Secretario General&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Eduardo Edmundo Salas Cerda</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Subsecretaria&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Paola Beatriz del Carmen Vidal Vergara</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Tesorera&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Gilda Victoria Schiaffino Arenas</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Protesorero&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Luis Alejandro Salas Cerda</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Directores&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Mariela de las Nieves Silva Leal</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Luz Marina Osorio Bahamondes</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Walter Francisco D&#xED;az Pasten</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &n